ZH: 这座城市有一座古老的碑。
EN: There is an ancient monument in this city.

ZH: 这块碑是为了纪念他们的祖先而立的。
EN: This monument was erected in honor of their ancestors.

ZH: 这块碑刻有许多古代的文字。
EN: This monument is inscribed with many ancient characters.

ZH: 每天都有很多游客来参观这座碑。
EN: Many tourists visit this monument every day.

ZH: 我们停在碑前，仔细地观察它。
EN: We stopped in front of the monument and examined it carefully.

ZH: 这座碑代表了这个城市的历史和文化。
EN: This monument symbolizes the history and culture of this city.

ZH: 在这座碑上，纪念了许多英雄。
EN: On this monument, many heroes are commemorated.

ZH: 这座碑是一座非常著名的地标。
EN: This monument is a very famous landmark.

ZH: 碑上的字迹虽已模糊，但依然可以辨认。
EN: The characters on the monument may be blurred, but still recognizable.

ZH: 这座碑的建造要花费很多财力和人力。
EN: The construction of this monument requires a lot of financial and human resources.

ZH: 碑文记录着这段历史。
EN: The inscription on the monument records this period of history.

ZH: 碑身雕刻着许多精美的花纹。
EN: The monument is carved with many exquisite patterns.

ZH: 这个大理石碑是一份珍贵的艺术品。
EN: This marble monument is a precious work of art.

ZH: 他们在碑旁默默祈祷。
EN: They prayed silently by the monument.

ZH: 这座大理石碑在夜晚显得更加庄严肃穆。
EN: The marble monument looks even more solemn in the night.

ZH: 碑下种植了许多美丽的鲜花。
EN: Many beautiful flowers are planted beneath the monument.

ZH: 这座碑是建筑师设计的杰作。
EN: This monument is a masterpiece designed by the architect.

ZH: 这座碑的历史可以追溯到几百年前。
EN: The history of this monument can be traced back hundreds of years.

ZH: 大家不约而同地聚集在碑前。
EN: Everyone gathered in front of the monument spontaneously.

ZH: 我们希望这座碑能永远留存下去。
EN: We hope that this monument will remain forever.
